list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Added old lib flag, since linker fails on Ubuntu.

task.summary: Default task
Added an option to build events that are not particle triggered.
Removed todo.
Fixed an error where the width of a channel (± 0.5) was not taken into account.
Fixed wrong type.
Added install path. Currently this is a static path.
Added badge for the license.
Added a method to check if the particle energies are within the required timings.
Fixed a bug where it would give a segerr if the file doesnt exist.
Changed the detector numeration of the dE rings to correspond to the real dE ring numbers.
Added a 2D graphical gate class in case it might be of use. If not, then it might be removed later.
Added time vs. energy spectra for particles.
Added dependency on GCAL for the PolygonGate.
Changes to make output files smaller.
Working on implementing the 2D gate.
Removed dependency on CGAL
Updated with MT buffer fetching. Hopefully this will reduce the memory requirements a lot.
Added a missing header giving build errors on Ubuntu.
Fixed an error that caused weird progress output to the terminal when running in npg mode.
A wrong index was used to fill the calibration histograms. I've also changed the time reference from the RF to LaBrF 0 (2x2 inch LaBr).
Changed the experimentalsetup file to reflect the setup of PR271.
Uncommented something. Don't know why it was commented. Doesn't matter.
Fixed the bug in issue #5.
Added an Interface class for the classes used to write to ROOT files.
Added a configuration structure to reduce the number of parameters needed to be passed around.
Removed some lines that is no longer needed.
Marked constructor as explicit
Various changes
Loads of updates!
Tiny fix!
Logger is now a build option
Usage of the MT buffered ROOT filler are now an optional feature. The functionality seems to be unstable on linux, but works fine with 6.18 and macOS
Fixed such that all refs. to spd are now hidded if logger is not enabled.
Added missing memory header
Added missing TTree dependency
Building all as static libraries
Root interface now static as well
Added old lib flag, since linker fails on Ubuntu.
Changed time ref. to be fast labr 0
Added an option to fill SQL server
